This is the code/documentation folder for the Citizen Cartography Lab THERMOGRAPHER project.

It is open source, free software, and is available under the MIT license (see LICENSE in this directory)

Read more about the project here: ...

/control-code/themographer.pde is the main code file, and runs on Arduino (http://arduino.cc)

